      <title>澳大利亚国民银行首席财务官：澳大利亚各大银行争相吸引商业银行家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/brewing-business-loans-rivalry-face-staff-crunch-nab-cfo-say</link>
